#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.reset_index.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.reset\\_index"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:1 of
msgid "Reset the index, or a level of it."
msgstr "重置索引，或索引的某个层级。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:3 of
msgid ""
"Reset the index of the DataFrame, and use the default one instead. If the"
" DataFrame has a MultiIndex, this method can remove one or more levels."
msgstr ""
"重置 DataFrame 的索引，并使用默认索引。如果 DataFrame 具有 MultiIndex，此"
"方法可以移除一个或多个层级。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:7 of
msgid ""
"Only remove the given levels from the index. Removes all levels by "
"default."
msgstr "仅从索引中移除指定的层级。默认移除所有层级。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:10 of
msgid ""
"Do not try to insert index into dataframe columns. This resets the index "
"to the default integer index."
msgstr "不要尝试将索引插入到 DataFrame 的列中。此操作将索引重置为默认的整数索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:13 of
msgid "Modify the DataFrame in place (do not create a new object)."
msgstr "就地修改 DataFrame（不创建新对象）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:15 of
msgid ""
"If the columns have multiple levels, determines which level the labels "
"are inserted into. By default it is inserted into the first level."
msgstr "如果列具有多个层级，则确定标签插入到哪一层级。默认插入到第一层级。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:19 of
msgid ""
"If the columns have multiple levels, determines how the other levels are "
"named. If None then the index name is repeated."
msgstr ""
"如果列具有多个层级，则确定其他层级的命名方式。如果为 None，则重复使用索引"
"名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:23 of
msgid "DataFrame with the new index or None if ``inplace=True``."
msgstr "具有新索引的 DataFrame，如果 ``inplace=True`` 则返回 None。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.set_index`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:29 of
msgid "Opposite of reset_index."
msgstr "reset_index 的反向操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.reindex`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:32 of
msgid "Change to new indices or expand indices."
msgstr "更改索引或扩展索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.reindex_like`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:35 of
msgid "Change to same indices as other DataFrame."
msgstr "将索引更改为与其他 DataFrame 相同。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:38 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:54 of
msgid ""
"When we reset the index, the old index is added as a column, and a new "
"sequential index is used:"
msgstr "当我们重置索引时，旧索引将作为一列添加，同时使用新的顺序索引："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:64 of
msgid ""
"We can use the `drop` parameter to avoid the old index being added as a "
"column:"
msgstr "我们可以使用 `drop` 参数来避免旧索引作为列添加："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:74 of
msgid "You can also use `reset_index` with `MultiIndex`."
msgstr "您也可以在 `MultiIndex` 上使用 `reset_index`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:99 of
msgid "If the index has multiple levels, we can reset a subset of them:"
msgstr "如果索引具有多个层级，我们可以重置其中的一部分："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:110 of
msgid ""
"If we are not dropping the index, by default, it is placed in the top "
"level. We can place it in another level:"
msgstr ""
"如果我们不删除索引，默认情况下它会被放置在顶层。我们可以将其放置在其他"
"层级："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:122 of
msgid ""
"When the index is inserted under another level, we can specify under "
"which one with the parameter `col_fill`:"
msgstr "当索引插入到另一个层级之下时，可以通过 `col_fill` 参数指定具体层级："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.df_reset_index:134 of
msgid "If we specify a nonexistent level for `col_fill`, it is created:"
msgstr "如果我们为 `col_fill` 指定一个不存在的层级，则会创建该层级："

